metadata.name: Frankness
metadata.description:
Female beauty is blooming, sensual, alluring, intoxicating, indomitable, attractive, charming, touching. Beauty is source of inspiration and the highest aesthetic pleasure. Beauty is an angel leading us into a world of endless pleasure. And it is the tempter, pushing us into vice. Beauty is yin and yang, the eternal struggle of light and darkness.

This beauty opens before you gently, a little shamefacedly. There is not a drop of vulgarity in her nakedness. This is a pure revelation, the discovery of a real hidden beauty.
